                            <comment id="14087284" author="remkop@yahoo.com" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 05:39:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The SLF4J API classes are not included in the Log4j2 distribution by design. Users need to get those separately. If you use Maven it will pull in the necessary dependencies automatically. Otherwise you need to do this manually.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We will update the Usage and Requirements pages to be more clear about this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14087681" author="remkop@yahoo.com" created="Wed, 6 Aug 2014 13:48:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Clarified documentation that SLF4J API jar is required when using log4j-slf4j-impl in revision 1616232.&lt;br/&gt;
Please verify and close.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
